				<h2>OUR NEIGHBORHOOD</h2>
				<p>We love our lives in Chicago and live in a very diverse neighborhood on the north side. We have a lot of family and friends in the city and we enjoy spending as much time with them as possible. Since Jeff’s family is all nearby, we get together with them for family dinners on a weekly basis. We care very much about our friends, who make up a diverse group and many of whom now have children of their own. Living in Chicago provides us with such great opportunities and the ability to have enriching, fun, child-friendly experiences with kids all the time.</p>
